name: Self-rule
description:
In ancient Greece, philosophers sought to unstring the mysteries of the universe in order to get a glimpse of the truth. 
They came up with an array of important ideas but most notably they came up with an idea that shaped our current civilization as we know it. 
They came up with democracy, "self-rule is fine" they said :)

### Task

Write a function ```_``` that outputs ```'self-rule is fine'``` without using any letters ```a-zA-Z```, numbers or hyphens ```'-'``` in your code.

### Code limit

Your code is limited to ```109``` characters

It is possible to do it in ```82``` characters ;)


Easier version here:
https://www.codewars.com/kata/65552e9756ea20197078a163
